"sistema di iniziare la migrazione da NethServer 7 a NethSecurity."

#: ../../migration.rst:74 25e6e03aead34900b27f1eca209bfbd5
msgid ""
"Select the target disk: choose the disk where NethSecurity will be "
"installed. Note that NethSecurity does not support RAID. If the original "
"NethServer 7 server has more than one disk, the other disks will remain "
"unchanged and unused during the migration process."
msgstr ""
