#: ../../migration.rst:77 530a1698fa03426b847790fb85f9cec9
msgid ""
"Confirm and start the process: after selecting the disk, click "
":guilabel:`Migrate` to confirm. The system will download the NethSecurity "
"image and write it to the selected disk. Subsequently, the system will "
"automatically reboot."
msgstr ""
"Confermare e avviare il processo: dopo aver selezionato il disco, fare clic "
